Kyriakos Charalambides. _Myths and History_. _Selected Poems_. Selected and translated from the Greek by David Connolly. With an introduction by Theofanis G. Stavrou. A Nostos Book, 26. Minneapolis, MN: Nostos Books, 2010. xvi, 101 p.

ISBN 0932963145; 9780932963147

